Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================OP============================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.11,0:02:10.36,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}任何人都在迷茫中寻觅答案
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.11,0:02:30.49,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}曾以为二人同心　时间也可支配
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.67,0:02:38.48,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}当岁月流逝　天空不再湛蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.68,0:02:43.57,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}心与心渐行渐远
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.08,0:02:51.37,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}周而复始　季节循环往复
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:57.94,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}愿时光　永远停留在那瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.20,0:03:04.13,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}二人仍迷茫着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.56,0:03:13.94,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}在天边寻找各自真爱的岁月…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================ED============================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.22,0:22:11.85,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,1500)}曾如此形影不离
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.17,0:22:20.94,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,2500)}黄昏却已变色…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.72,0:22:37.28,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}平凡的温柔　让你远去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.53,0:22:45.01,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}被抛弃的心灵　四处彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.33,0:22:53.24,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}这份失落　如果就是生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.44,0:22:57.52,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}我愿在夜空下　从此闭上双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.80,0:23:06.55,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}曾形影不离　黄昏却已变色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.80,0:23:17.77,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}{\be1}至少让我在月光下　静静入眠…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Avant============================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.29,0:00:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 传闻中的大天使？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.36,0:00:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 仍然没有动静
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.28,0:00:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地上满是中子干扰器
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.61,0:00:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电波状况糟到不能再糟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.61,0:00:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她还睡得正香吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.15,0:00:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.18,0:00:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 这次少加了5%摩卡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.11,0:00:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这味道我喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.32,0:00:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.41,0:00:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从现在起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.70,0:01:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对地球军新造舰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.32,0:01:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大天使号展开作战行动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.41,0:01:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的是对敌舰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.35,0:01:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,及其搭载机动战士进行战力评价
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.87,0:01:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失手打坏了怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.03,0:01:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…真那样也没法子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.18,0:01:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那艘船是逃过克鲁泽队追捕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈尔巴顿的第八舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.87,0:01:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不惜牺牲全军去保护的船
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.03,0:01:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别忘记这点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.80,0:01:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.51,0:01:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 祝各位好运
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.48,0:01:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员登机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.99,0:01:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 咖啡香心情就好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.29,0:01:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 该去打仗了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Main============================
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.66,0:03:30.04,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1184,576)}{\fad(500,500)}{\bord3\shad1\be20\an3\fs60}热砂战场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.51,0:03:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校 今天先到这儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.09,0:03:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的上了天才知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.63,0:03:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.03,0:03:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉也恢复了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天说不定就得上路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.81,0:03:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好是今天能完成…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.42,0:04:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 穿穿好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.22,0:04:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这副睡眼惺忪的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.80,0:04:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了舰桥又要被巴基露露中尉训斥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.55,0:04:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉这么晚来打搅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.17,0:04:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 一直没时间和你好好说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.69,0:04:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于白天的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.84,0:04:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你起来下好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说他们有婚约
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.27,0:04:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没定 还只是刚开始谈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.98,0:04:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么区别
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.07,0:04:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾最近有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.20,0:04:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前虽然谈不上讨厌基拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:04:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是讨厌调整人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.16,0:05:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾低一年级
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.44,0:05:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过和你同一个社团
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.14,0:05:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校里也已经见到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.30,0:05:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她以前就说基拉很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.15,0:05:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但愿别发展成奇怪的关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.11,0:05:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.23,0:05:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船体的排热
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.73,0:05:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是经过黑洞排气系统进行冷却
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.63,0:05:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要骗过卫星的红外线探测
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.20,0:05:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题应该不大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.24,0:05:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都用不了雷达
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.61,0:05:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.31,0:05:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换班来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.77,0:05:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么晚才来 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.62,0:05:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.35,0:05:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中子干扰器吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.90,0:05:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能去除吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.84,0:06:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.20,0:06:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被埋进地底很深
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总数也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.16,0:06:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能的话早干了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.64,0:06:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电波外加能源供应
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.17,0:06:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影响虽然挺大的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 总比核弹满天飞好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.55,0:06:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核打击尤尼乌斯7号之后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.20,0:06:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被核报复 地球现在早没了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.83,0:06:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没异常吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.41,0:06:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船体的扭曲数据有了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.54,0:06:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.01,0:06:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据简易测定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.74,0:06:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应力扭曲还在正常范围内
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.86,0:06:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,详细…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.40,0:06:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉 还停留在无重力下的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.48,0:06:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.60,0:06:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重力场内有暗斑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.16,0:06:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是地下空洞的影响吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.00,0:06:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.71,0:07:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据战前资料
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.31,0:07:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道准确位置
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.72,0:07:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附近地区 有石油和天然气废矿坑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.91,0:07:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是随便哪里都能一屁股坐下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.08,0:07:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.79,0:07:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.31,0:07:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰 遭到激光照射
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.78,0:07:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对照 确认为索敌瞄准
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二级战斗状态
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.98,0:07:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复 二级战斗状态
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.42,0:07:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.86,0:07:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.21,0:07:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.33,0:08:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会再让任何人死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.29,0:08:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.48,0:08:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.86,0:08:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀光那些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.32,0:08:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报告情况
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.56,0:08:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一波导弹攻击 6发
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.24,0:08:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獾阵炮迎击中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击来自沙丘背面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.12,0:08:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法确认发射位置
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下令进入一级战斗状态
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.01,0:08:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎启动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.25,0:08:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗拉戈少校和大和少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在座机内待命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗拉戈少校能出击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.57,0:08:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反光束爆雷装填
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.19,0:09:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,释放中子干扰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.11,0:09:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.22,0:09:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.81,0:09:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航空队 开始进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.27,0:09:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能飞就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.48,0:09:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您就别强人所难了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.42,0:09:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光装弹药都来不及
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.48,0:09:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5点方向 敌影3
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.07,0:09:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认为扎夫特战斗直升机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导弹接近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.54,0:09:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丢失敌影
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.92,0:09:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射热诱弹 迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.12,0:09:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.56,0:09:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强袭出击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.24,0:09:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.16,0:09:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 还没…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.75,0:09:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快开舱门
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.71,0:10:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人的位置和兵力都不明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.64,0:10:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出击命令也没下达
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候还说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.43,0:10:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快开舱门
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.56,0:10:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去干掉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.24,0:10:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.66,0:10:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.87,0:10:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说得难听 但只有让他去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.49,0:10:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰船行动不便
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.37,0:10:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让强袭出击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.06,0:10:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开舱门 强袭出击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.66,0:10:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱逐敌战斗直升机
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意重力影响
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.75,0:10:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连接弹射器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.09,0:10:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,APU 上线
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.30,0:10:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮袭者 待命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.22,0:10:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火器 能量包正常
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.43,0:10:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路线清空 请强袭出击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.10,0:11:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.77,0:11:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了 那就是X-105强袭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.65,0:11:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出动BuCUE 看看反应
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.98,0:12:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.89,0:12:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.86,0:12:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TMFA-802 扎夫特军机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BuCUE
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.94,0:12:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BuCUE？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天上威风惯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.44,0:12:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里BuCUE才是王者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.22,0:12:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛮锤飞弹 发射
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.03,0:12:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会击中强袭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.65,0:12:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有相转移装甲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.19,0:12:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.62,0:12:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.33,0:12:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样不是办法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.87,0:12:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 发射蛮锤飞弹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉 躲开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.42,0:13:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉哟 指挥官不拿机师的命当回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.19,0:13:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是 出于信赖？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.20,0:13:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.82,0:13:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是台很棒的机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶员的技术也不算坏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.74,0:13:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但终究是人型
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.16,0:13:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙漠里赢不了BuCUE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.41,0:13:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校的空中霸王呢 还不能出击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.61,0:13:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会这一招
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.06,0:14:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,着地压如果不足
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.57,0:14:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调整到足不就是了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.99,0:14:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预估流失的着地压
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.55,0:14:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩擦系数设定为砂粒状负20
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.95,0:14:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短短数分钟内
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.87,0:14:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将运动程序调整为砂地仕样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.35,0:14:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是自然人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.97,0:15:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想碰…大天使号
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.03,0:15:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电告莱塞普号
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.05,0:15:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主炮炮击敌舰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他杀了涅拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.62,0:15:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空中霸王 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.07,0:15:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西南方向热源靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.08,0:15:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是炮击！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.42,0:15:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,升空 紧急回避
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.83,0:16:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.93,0:16:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西南方向 推定20公里处
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.92,0:16:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰攻击装备无法回击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去做激光指向
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.44,0:16:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用导弹招呼它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在才开始搜索敌人也来不及
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.75,0:16:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总比被动挨打好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.26,0:16:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚持住哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.34,0:16:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗拉戈机 待命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.61,0:16:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路线清空 系统正常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.64,0:16:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报告里没有提到这机体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.43,0:16:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二波接近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.73,0:17:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回避 全员防备冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.53,0:17:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直击弹道！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.74,0:17:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.94,0:17:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会保护
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.65,0:17:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会保护我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.17,0:17:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.40,0:18:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强袭的能量 进入危险区
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.09,0:18:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熔岩炮用多了吗 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.40,0:18:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是个怪物样的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.19,0:18:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但根据情报快没电了才对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.55,0:18:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 你死定了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.49,0:18:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为涅拉姆报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.77,0:18:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掩护 大天使号慢速前进
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.49,0:18:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.88,0:18:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种情况开火的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.20,0:18:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强袭的装甲也会失效
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:19:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机动战士驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.21,0:19:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想死的话 就按我说得做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.84,0:19:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地图标志处有陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.34,0:19:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把BuCUE引去那里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.81,0:19:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.94,0:19:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反抗组织？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长 是沙漠拂晓的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.10,0:19:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想救地球军的机动战士？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.74,0:20:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上钩了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.54,0:20:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为鱼饵够上等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.69,0:20:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有信他们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.44,0:20:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.02,0:21:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.78,0:21:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗目的已经达成
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.84,0:21:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集合残存部队
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.68,0:21:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.92,0:21:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗拉戈少校来电
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.65,0:21:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现敌母舰 但放弃攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.72,0:21:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人母舰是莱塞普号
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.20,0:21:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱塞普号？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.85,0:21:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复 敌人母舰是莱塞普号
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.04,0:21:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在返航 以上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.66,0:21:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱塞普号是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.01,0:21:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是安德鲁·巴尔菲鲁特的母舰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.99,0:22:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人是 沙漠之虎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Next============================
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.04,0:23:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未能保护的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.99,0:23:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与他背负的其他责任一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.53,0:23:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令基拉的内心渐渐发生变化
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.63,0:23:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙漠战场上的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.20,0:23:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为保护自己的未来而战
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.93,0:23:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你死我活的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.15,0:23:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让孩子们看见怎样的明天？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.25,0:23:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 机动战士高达SEED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.71,0:23:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「卡嘉莉再来」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.33,0:23:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞向新的舞台 高达








